<item>
            <title>[SOLR-13080] TermsQParserPlugin automaton method fails to sort input</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-13080</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The contract for Automata.makeStringUnion is that the input is sorted. As BytesRef implements Comparable. The simplest fix would probably to make&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Arrays.sort(bytesRefs);&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The first line of automaton&apos;s makeFilter method in TermsQParserPlugin.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
